{"tid":1324904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳伯有嘢講！重新開始絕食","createTime":"2019-07-16T16:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T12:57:42.000Z","uid":266668,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f33def50e74697a7010632b277f0992fd1e81834","tid":1324904,"uid":266668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:47:38.000Z","msg":"以下係錄音，我再轉為文字方便大家睇<br />\n陳伯:<br />\n青年人你哋好啊，我係陳伯，我尋晚精神開始衰退。但唔緊要，經過醫生嘅照料今晚我已經可以翻到大本營。我亦都會繼續同大家一齊絕食，但絕食方式同以前唔同。以往我係全程絕食，但今次我有特殊任務係更加重要，分身不暇嘅關係我選擇一段段時間地絕食，有時間我就會返嚟呢度同大家一齊。希望大家諒解我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次只係絕食形式唔同，唔係全程直落。只要我一有時間 就會同戰友講:我幾時翻黎。<span style=\"color: red;\">所以大家唔使擔心我，我而家一切正常。</span>我亦都可以撐落去！<span style=\"color: red;\">關心我就夠！擔心就唔需要啦 唔同㗎。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家抗爭嘅時候唔好使用武力，掌握住唔好超越政府同警察嘅底線，免得佢哋捉住我哋嘅痛腳！<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地抗爭要講究策略，抗爭係長期嘅，所以我哋唔好作無謂嘅犧牲！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望我有最後一口氣同大家 同青年人繼續同行 爭取民主 自由 公義 ！維護法治！大家共同努力 合作，做好呢件事。如果我有咩做得唔好，唔緊要㗎青年人可以俾啲意見我，等我更加輕鬆面對而家惡劣嘅環境。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我哋一定要珍惜我哋嘅生命同力量</span></span>"},{"pid":"2eb36b3687f6a02b80b8a610429843fd6eed8265","tid":1324904,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb13a97138a1bb6fd6393a86d4860de691ab1b13","tid":1324904,"uid":78913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:49:30.000Z","msg":"支持陳仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55081e9be56680adb164c0b75eb23eaf57c49046","tid":1324904,"uid":266668,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:50:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bsg02xY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBsg02xY.png&h=967e8a6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb30868497fa7e28f6399b2901175071bb2bc313","tid":1324904,"uid":273163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:51:47.000Z","msg":"陳伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a55e4c8847b7782dce3db9fc668803d3579ff8f","tid":1324904,"uid":266668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:52:43.000Z","msg":"轉自tg gp:<br />\n《招募絕食者支援團隊》<br />\n<br />\n各位，香港很多朋友也正運用不同方式抗爭中，我們的絕食運動已持續了超過170小時了，我們的絕食者體力即將進入臨界點。但至今，政府還沒有正面地回應我們的訴求，所以我們需要大家支持我們的絕食行動，協助絕食者基本的照顧，陪伴有需要的朋友，及回應來探訪的公眾等。<br />\n<br />\n我們希望招幕每天的場地支援人員：<br />\n- 到場協助絕食者表達絶食行動的意念<br />\n- 派發傳單/叫市民睇日記等<br />\n- 情緒支援/陪伴到場又有情緒的市民<br />\n- 幫手紀錄每位絕食者的身體status<br />\n- 每日兩更：12:00-14:00/ 17:00-21:00<br />\n- 每更希望有3-4人<br />\n<br />\n絕食者照顧team<br />\n- 早上了解絕食者狀況 <br />\n- 幫手清潔絕食者現場<br />\n- 陪絕食者去廁所<br />\n- 晚上9:00陪絕食者去沖涼<br />\n- 每日三段時間： 10:00am / 13:00pm-14:00pm/ 21:00-23:00pm <br />\n<br />\n*不需要每天到，也未必要留一整更，但希望集氣，讓絕食者有更多支援～<br />\n<br />\n可以幫手的朋友請填寫以下表格，以便我們再與你聯絡：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/AByV3fw7ez11f7B3A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FAByV3fw7ez11f7B3A&d=4wcocBccBPvk8MIeFEbr%2BVKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=b7e8addd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/AByV3fw7ez11f7B3A</a>"},{"pid":"e6002323d769e569edd424664ba6120ca1177835","tid":1324904,"uid":268131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a07a5cb9bd86dc2ae4f02fc5f5f13a683830e78","tid":1324904,"uid":97678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3a6cdec3294de968330f7613d0200f81c579c5","tid":1324904,"uid":266668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:09:35.000Z","msg":"伯伯七十幾歲啦！佢話最後一口氣嗰句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真心好sad<br />\n所以我地！有力出力，老人家都企出黎，你冇理由唔出掛 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">721見</span>"},{"pid":"add8e251e44963f263296d9061ace0c29bc68ef3","tid":1324904,"uid":9640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ikZxS6J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FikZxS6J.png&h=c66af2bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，騎劫一下<br />\n請照顧同行長者<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n1.）撤回逃犯修例<br />\n2.）撤回暴動定性<br />\n3.）無條件釋放被捕示威者<br />\n4.）追究警方暴力濫權<br />\n5.）我要雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">陳伯同一眾絕食人士身體健康！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有！7月21日都要出黎！</span></span>"},{"pid":"2af9ee4226492631efc45b99bbb27ead9d283c29","tid":1324904,"uid":202889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:23:48.000Z","msg":"其實伯伯都係想支持我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如轉移下目標<br />\n叫伯伯去下茶樓  社區中心同其他老友記宣傳<br />\n比個目標伯伯做 總好過絕食傷身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3758aee634e07772cf34fbdfa0c219ed2f7636b","tid":1324904,"uid":191552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:26:10.000Z","msg":"唔理衝唔衝 721金鐘！"},{"pid":"309205b3737532dac1bcfc0f95b1884e3504ea4c","tid":1324904,"uid":191552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:26:24.000Z","msg":"唔理衝唔衝 721金鐘！"},{"pid":"0d571e1885fd3b3da750edfd5b165756c1f70e7e","tid":1324904,"uid":259675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />